            "id": 6132450,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 慧友(5484)股價殺至跌停，跌停價48.55元，成交2,845張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>慧友(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5484:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5484\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5484-TW</a>)29日13:17下跌5.35元，股價跌停報48.55元，委賣152張，成交2,845張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為CCD電子攝影機、影像處理器。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>慧友(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5484:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5484\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5484-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲43.73%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.14%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-298 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-300 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+2 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6132450",
